{"tid":1098421,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【懷念第一把劍】王嘉爾爆喊：冇時間陪爸爸","createTime":"2019-04-09T04:58:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T01:29:34.000Z","uid":193951,"like":2,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"228b5f5cd3d56119f2cd0aa92fd88b3aa278ca33","tid":1098421,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T04:58:55.000Z","msg":"歌手王嘉爾（Jackson）近日參加內地真人騷節目《這！就是原創》，他在最新一集中忍不住爆喊，皆因曾經是香港劍擊選手的他回憶起練習劍擊的日子。其中一位選手所寫的歌，令Jackson感同身受，他坦言現在擁有好多物質，但他最懷念爸爸送的第一把劍，他說：「我第一把劍是爸爸給的，很爛的、也沒有牌子。我慢慢愈來愈好了，爸爸也愈來愈老了，我們的距離愈來愈開了，我拿了很多第一名，但才發現不是最開心的，最珍貴的不是我穿去奧運的衣服，就是我那把劍。」更哽咽感觸道：「我沒有甚麼時間陪爸爸一起過。」要以紙巾拭淚。好多粉絲都心痛年紀輕輕的Jackson，工作十分忙碌，甚少有時間跟家人見面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2chpWN6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2chpWN6.jpg&h=7279d50a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王嘉爾講起爸爸畀佢嘅第一把劍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B9QOD1B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB9QOD1B.jpg&h=52482dd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當年嘅王嘉爾好青澀！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TpvKWOi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTpvKWOi.jpg&h=7ab4dc12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講到眼濕濕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z3au7UZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ3au7UZ.jpg&h=50bf889f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n雖然攞咗好多第一名...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QLWRBOk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQLWRBOk.jpg&h=b659c6a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但最重要嘅都係家人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fOYXxmO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfOYXxmO.jpg&h=60fc1bfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講到爆喊！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Rki1fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Rki1fa.jpg&h=62b7bdd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n希望王嘉爾嚟緊抽到多啲時間陪爸爸啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嘎嘎真係好孝順 睇到咸左😭"},{"pid":"60b7a1331bf39dbaa72b8061ed67a66384787037","tid":1098421,"uid":208486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T05:01:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b34be89521b5f926c7ae1a3eb8ba0d63bc1dc0","tid":1098421,"uid":46435,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T05:06:03.000Z","msg":"食食下飯咸左出黎 好心痛嘎嘎.."},{"pid":"8a8bb9e24853ec5b226a728fbb0332d21bec91c7","tid":1098421,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T05:06:06.000Z","msg":"嘎嘎別哭😥😥😥"},{"pid":"54190aa12379f93835540413b8ad5b09f2cd1a8f","tid":1098421,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"02b34be89521b5f926c7ae1a3eb8ba0d63bc1dc0","tid":1098421,"uid":46435,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T05:06:03.000Z","msg":"食食下飯咸左出黎 好心痛嘎嘎.."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T05:13:53.000Z","msg":"見到嘎嘎喊 我哋成班Jacky都好心痛..."},{"pid":"1c2ac463c16e3fe46b87a5f9f168307886f4ac0c","tid":1098421,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"8a8bb9e24853ec5b226a728fbb0332d21bec91c7","tid":1098421,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T05:06:06.000Z","msg":"嘎嘎別哭😥😥😥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T05:14:33.000Z","msg":"孝順的嘎嘎真的很難不讓人喜歡..."},{"pid":"09e053f8d21b976b9a2201a654c3cf78aa7be224","tid":1098421,"uid":38216,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T05:29:52.000Z","msg":"講到佢老豆rip咗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f548142b0987f776e00cb6f5e91f3206d86ae5d3","tid":1098421,"uid":21398,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"09e053f8d21b976b9a2201a654c3cf78aa7be224","tid":1098421,"uid":38216,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T05:29:52.000Z